      "date": "2013-11-26 11:13:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/3c3a06c8-5689-11e3-9288-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  4 tests failed: conf-sanity, replay-single, sanityn, sanity.",
